name: "Comrades pace" dry run
description:
Proof to myself -- and perhaps my likely running partner Charlene Nixon -- that I _can_ run at our target Comrades pace! 🙂

Gorgeous weather!  Toronto's lilacs are fully in bloom, giving me itchy eyes, and a big smile!

Definitely felt the high-volume week by the end, but feeling confident about the big day June 8
